<item>
            <title>[SPR-7959] Update AbstractPdfView to use com.itextpdf.* package</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-7959</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The class org.springframework.web.servlet.view.document.AbstractPdfView references the iText PDF library using the package com.lowagie.&lt;b&gt;.  The most recent version of iText uses the package com.itextpdf.&lt;/b&gt; instead of com.lowagie.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The current workaround is to use an older version of iText, but it would be nice to have this updated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
